channel.title: Compile Error
channel.description:
Hey guys , i was fixing my claw spec as it only hit 2 hits and meant to be 4 although i got this error when doing it..
source\server\model\players\CombatAssistant.java:3736: error: unreachable statem ent c.doubleHit = true; ^ Note: Some input files use unchecked or unsafe operations. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:unchecked for details. 1 error Press any key to continue . . .
Please can someone explain this and help me resolve this in as much detail thanks!

item.title: Compile Error
item.dc:creator: @b00mz1029 b00mz1029
item.description:
@b00mz1029 wrote:

No that will ruin your server, you’ll have to undo that, it just can’t understand the c.(whatever) statement, it doesn’t understand “c” try to copy another thing with the “c.” infront of it and edit all of the stuff you want in.
